---
config:
  theme: base
  themeVariables:
    primaryColor: "#4A90D9"
    primaryTextColor: "#000"
    lineColor: "#555"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant M as main.c
    participant D as demo.c
    participant ADC as ADC 模块
    participant PWM as PWM 模块
    participant IMU as MS901M
    participant MB as Modbus

    Note over M: 系统上电

    M->>M: HAL_Init()
    M->>M: sys_stm32_clock_init()<br/>168MHz 主频
    M->>M: delay_init(168)
    M->>M: usart_init(115200)<br/>调试串口

    M->>D: demo_run()

    D->>ADC: adc_init()
    Note right of ADC: ADC1 初始化<br/>5通道 12bit<br/>PC0/PC1/PC2/PC3/PA1

    D->>PWM: pwm_init(19999, 83)
    Note right of PWM: TIM1/3/4/8<br/>50Hz PWM<br/>10路输出

    D->>IMU: atk_ms901m_init(115200)
    Note right of IMU: USART3 初始化<br/>等待传感器响应

    D->>MB: modbus_init()
    Note right of MB: FreeModbus 初始化<br/>从站 0x01<br/>USART2 9600 8N1

    Note over D: ══ 系统就绪 ══

    loop 主循环 (每 5ms)
        D->>IMU: get_attitude() / get_gyro()
        IMU-->>D: Roll/Pitch/Yaw/GyroXYZ
        D->>MB: set_register_float()
        D->>MB: modbus_process()
        MB->>ADC: update_sensors()
        ADC-->>MB: 模拟量 + 电压 + 原始值
        MB->>MB: eMBPoll()
    end
